_sText:
I found this on my computer, and it wasn't uploaded here so I decided to do it myself.

It is an open map (Still with mid-range combat) where Terrorists must either blow up the place or kill all the Counter-Terrorists.

I don't know who is the original creator of it, but I would be glad if a name is given.

Can run 15 vs 15 matchs.

Enjoy!
